{{ 'component-slider.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<div class="tw-container tw-mx-auto tw-max-w-[1400px] tw-py-16 md:tw-px-12 tw-px-4">
  <slider-component class="slider-mobile-gutter scroll-trigger animate--slide-in">
    <div id="Slider-{{ section.id }}" role="list" class="tw-grid tw-grid-cols-1 tw-gap-8 md:tw-grid-cols-3 tw-mx-auto">
      <div
        id="Slide-{{ section.id }}-0"
        class="slider__slide scroll-trigger animate--slide-in"
        data-cascade
        style="--animation-order: 0;"
      >
        <div class="tw-flex tw-gap-3 tw-text-lg tw-font-semibold tw-items-center">
          <div class="tw-h-10 tw-w-10 tw-items-center tw-justify-center tw-rounded-2xl tw-bg-sky-100 tw-flex tw-flex-none">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="tw-h-6 tw-w-6 tw-text-sky-300"
            >
              <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M9.785 6l8.215 8.215l-2.054 2.054a5.81 5.81 0 1 1 -8.215 -8.215l2.054 -2.054z" /><path d="M4 20l3.5 -3.5" /><path d="M15 4l-3.5 3.5" /><path d="M20 9l-3.5 3.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          Plug & Play
        </div>
        <div class="tw-mt-2 tw-text-base tw-leading-7 tw-text-gray-600">
          Mit einfacher Plug & Play Installation können Sie Ihr Balkonkraftwerk einfach in eine Steckdose stecken.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="slider__slide scroll-trigger animate--slide-in"
        id="Slide-{{ section.id }}-1"
        data-cascade
        style="--animation-order: 1;"
      >
        <div class="tw-flex tw-gap-3 tw-text-lg tw-font-semibold tw-items-center">
          <div class="tw-h-10 tw-w-10 tw-items-center tw-justify-center tw-rounded-xl tw-bg-sky-100 tw-flex tw-flex-none">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="tw-h-6 tw-w-6 tw-text-sky-300"
            >
              <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M19 10l-7 -7l-9 9h2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h7.5" /><path d="M9 21v-6a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h2c.661 0 1.248 .32 1.612 .815" /><path d="M19 14l-2 4h4l-2 4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          Kompakte Bauweise
        </div>
        <div class="tw-mt-2 tw-text-base tw-leading-7 tw-text-gray-600">
          Die platzsparende Gestaltung ermöglicht es Ihnen in begrenzten Raumverhältnissen die Vorteile erneuerbarer
          Energie zu nutzen.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="slider__slide scroll-trigger animate--slide-in"
        id="Slide-{{ section.id }}-2"
        data-cascade
        style="--animation-order: 2;"
      >
        <div class="tw-flex tw-gap-3 tw-text-lg tw-font-semibold tw-items-center">
          <div class="tw-h-10 tw-w-10 tw-items-center tw-justify-center tw-rounded-xl tw-bg-sky-100 tw-flex tw-flex-none">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="tw-h-6 tw-w-6 tw-text-sky-300"
            >
              <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M15 11v.01" /><path d="M5.173 8.378a3 3 0 1 1 4.656 -1.377" /><path d="M16 4v3.803a6.019 6.019 0 0 1 2.658 3.197h1.341a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v2a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-1.342c-.336 .95 -.907 1.8 -1.658 2.473v2.027a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 -3 0v-.583a6.04 6.04 0 0 1 -1 .083h-4a6.04 6.04 0 0 1 -1 -.083v.583a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 -3 0v-2l0 -.027a6 6 0 0 1 4 -10.473h2.5l4.5 -3h0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          Niedrige Stromkosten
        </div>
        <div class="tw-mt-2 tw-text-base tw-leading-7 tw-text-gray-600">
          Den Strom selbst erzeugen und Ihre Abhängigkeit von teurem Netzstrom reduzieren, um Energiekosten zu senken.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </slider-component>
</div>
